{"tid":703243,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"VISA：研究參與港鐵QR Code入閘系統投標","createTime":"2018-06-15T14:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T03:43:19.000Z","uid":27047,"like":72,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"f98c19861651d36d8206f32ed74bd393b58e7621","tid":703243,"uid":27047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1529048125_26aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1529048125_26aa.jpg&h=1682c50f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nVISA香港區總經理戴嘉倩指出，香港本身擁有龐大用家使用非接觸式支付工具，例如非接觸式信用卡及Apple Pay等，絕對有條件在各項交通工具開放支付系統，即一個收款器（POS）容納多個支付工具。<br />\n<br />\n被問到港鐵（066）入閘機應否開放支付系統時，她認為在現時香港萬事俱備，完全沒有難度，原因是與香港相似的倫敦市早於2014年時已開放支付系統，信用卡亦可以入閘，不用買票或增值Oyster卡。<br />\n<br />\n她認為，當港鐵見到外地城市的先進後，將會考慮開放支付系統，她又認為開放與不開放，是商業問題多於技術問題，原因是現時網絡已非常先進，「10年封閉式支付系統較快，呢個係事實，但10年後的今日，開放式支付系統已經一樣優勝」。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵二維碼（QR Code）閘機系統招標正展開前期工作，戴嘉倩指<span style=\"color: red;\">VISA已提交計劃書的資格預審申請，未來亦有興趣參與，但相信最成功的系統仍是開放式非接觸式支付系統</span>。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦交通局商務分析部主管Jeremy Itzcovitz指出，多年前該市亦研究過在交通工具使用二維碼，但發現在入閘前需要諸多準備，不便利乘客及出現人龍，故此屬意使用非接觸開放式支付。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Visa 會唔會一次過交哂EMV QR, NFC payment solution比 MTR<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f451be771f187f13c30f5d222fc44432a89d6219","tid":703243,"uid":100131,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 越做越退化係咩玩法"},{"pid":"2b40c91b9534260995d8d8ce31699616f6cecffc","tid":703243,"uid":27047,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"f451be771f187f13c30f5d222fc44432a89d6219","tid":703243,"uid":100131,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 越做越退化係咩玩法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:40:54.000Z","msg":"咁係MTR仆街啫，剩係俾QR code 玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caddbcb5f8d28a293872360549f99ce41771ea0d","tid":703243,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"腦生係屎忽"},{"pid":"d6927ce8a1b2b806398df8f4fc0e8dcb1b6fb971","tid":703243,"uid":100131,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"開放apple pay, google play...外國遊客黎香港唔洗買飛, 就咁do 就可以, 增加旅遊優勢嘅野唔做, 要去做QR code..."},{"pid":"c60a70ec99c87037da5c0c19477d4d24ad29065a","tid":703243,"uid":27047,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:44:40.000Z","msg":"Visa 自己都話 NFC contactless 好過QR code<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc86f027fa2e71f36203a476f9cf4467ff7885df","tid":703243,"uid":1524,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"要同大陸接軌，靜喺照顧大陸個market就夠。 佢哋喺咁諗嘢"},{"pid":"a30bc46cc3dc4178efb11336419522e7315c7a69","tid":703243,"uid":27047,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"cc86f027fa2e71f36203a476f9cf4467ff7885df","tid":703243,"uid":1524,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"要同大陸接軌，靜喺照顧大陸個market就夠。 佢哋喺咁諗嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"可能Visa 係第一個比MTR DQ 嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282b65d186c9c13e680de0bf14ad1c860e4594c9","tid":703243,"uid":37808,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"大陸好多都用nfc喇 港鐵仲用qr code<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d384bcbf9401484ca731620b7f091f82834f6f2","tid":703243,"uid":26602,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"282b65d186c9c13e680de0bf14ad1c860e4594c9","tid":703243,"uid":37808,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:49:1